{"tid":937484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人執到八達通T-T","createTime":"2018-12-11T14:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T15:42:14.000Z","uid":221391,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"900dfc3609c494f1480d5753e158371a6789e896","tid":937484,"uid":221391,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"我今個月八號係機場T2或者係由東涌開往機場嘅s1巴士（大概早上6點左右）度唔見左八達通⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n如果有人係機場T2 或者機場範圍 或者上述巴士班次嘅下層執到八達通，可唔可以比我對下係咪我嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個八達通係學生八達通黎，放係一個粉紅色嘅八達通套入面。仲有張poly學生證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTo執到我張八達通嘅人<br />\n你用晒我果幾廿蚊唔緊要啊，我唔想比多$70+110補領八達通同學生證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求下你比番張八達通同學生證我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想year4得番一個sem仲要比$110補領<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nThank you sooooooo much!!!!!"},{"pid":"962a1bab70271c04649b2a50386f4bce68fb34cb","tid":937484,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫你推"},{"pid":"962e2bfcee1ee72c5e8870bf46977130b6a8f7ef","tid":937484,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"冇㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306cb3458a5a02e9ae41a3b644b642fc752edd2c","tid":937484,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T15:00:55.000Z","msg":"過咗3日先po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be01528f49a45b48c7d112207d67bdcb115f890","tid":937484,"uid":48294,"lik